label: BinaryFile
comment: A computer file or program stored in a binary format.

datatypeProperties.comment: Access information, expressed as text, for this specified binary file, such as security and download parameters.
A name of an author, expressed as text, of this specified binary file.
The code specifying the character set for this specified binary file.
A textual description of this specified binary file.
The code specifying the encoding of this specified binary file.
The file name, expressed as text, of this specified binary file. Deprecated - Use Binary File. Name. Text instead.
A unique identifier for this specified binary file.
A binary object included in this specified binary file.
The code specifying the Multipurpose Internet Mail Extensions (MIME) type for this specified binary file.
The measure of the size of this specified binary file.
A title, expressed as text, for this specified binary file.
The unique Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) for this specified binary file.
The unique version identifier for this specified binary file.

objectProperties.comment: The specified period when access to this binary file is available.

referencedBy.comment: A specified binary file used to create this valuation breakdown statement.
A file containing a specified binary representation of a logo associated with this trade party.
A binary file presentation specified for this trade product.
A specified binary file used to read this valuation breakdown statement.
A binary file related to this specified observation.
The value for this product characteristic expressed in a binary file.
